00:03:37.540 --> 00:03:42.200
The agreement was established in the Cold
War era, when a group of scientists from 12

00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:45.500
different nations convinced the UN to institute
the “International Geophysical Year”,

00:03:45.500 --> 00:03:46.500
an event designed to promote scientific research
in Antarctica.

00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:48.400
It’s success contributed to the Treaty we
know today.

